- Update to version 0.9.31:
  * Refactoring: QuirksSet renamed to QuirksDb, to simplify documentation
  * UsbDeviceInfo: properly handle empty Manufacturer or ProductName
  * UsbDeviceInfo.MfgAndProduct sting replaced with UsbDeviceInfo
  * Preliminary Support for HWID-Based Quirks
  * HWID quirks integrated with the UsbTransport
  * Added HWID quirks for Xerox B210
  * Added HWID quirks for Xerox B205 and B215
  * Man page updated (HWID quirks explained)
  * Small refactoring of quirks handling
  * Quirks prioritization algorithm updated to match the documentation
  * Paths refactored (preparation to make them configurable)
  * Accept textWithLanguage for many printer attrs where text is expected
  * Added program options to control file/directory placement
  * Fix handling of usb-send-delay-threshold quirk
  * Fixed a error message formatting

